{"tid":2222742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洗米嫂重擊Mandy Lieu高調出山 一句K.O.最強小三：我…….!","createTime":"2020-09-29T09:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:34:03.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b83b346bea189863a6b757b72db3e42cd77b0ee6","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"洗米嫂Heidi（陳慧玲）同最強小三Mandy Lieu為爭奪太陽娛樂集團老闆洗米華（周焯華），不時招來招往，早前有傳去年Mandy Lieu收3億分手費，以後長留英國，以為搶米戰勝負已定，點知突傳出洗米華和Mandy Lieu復合兼在泰國合體，最近Mandy Lieu又高調出山轉行做專欄作家，動作多多，看似佔盡上峰，實質係點呢？不時在IG發布近況的洗米嫂，回應網民問題時，一句&hellip;.，完美K.O.最強小三﹗"},{"pid":"743aa761277e8a18b9e0daca9a8083bb0c3d4245","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/heidi.honey_101561561_556955205251137_1764873172808629933_n_19863462815f72dc85220bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fheidi.honey_101561561_556955205251137_1764873172808629933_n_19863462815f72dc85220bf.jpg&h=dac745b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前洗米嫂不時晒同老公洗米華的甜蜜合照。"},{"pid":"e7f9ae88a57e56809817607bb206fda02263e479","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/heidi.honey_101084478_2573452346089223_2356432815929482021_n_7412451815f72dc883e341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fheidi.honey_101084478_2573452346089223_2356432815929482021_n_7412451815f72dc883e341.jpg&h=a9d67bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為細女及老公華哥大搞生日會，席間甜蜜蜜。"},{"pid":"74a4f80eaa892d92390cd9f6f8da54f5595c352d","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/4bd3d3e5-ef5d-484b-9481-51e95e94dbc5_9921248775f72dc3282991.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F4bd3d3e5-ef5d-484b-9481-51e95e94dbc5_9921248775f72dc3282991.jpeg&h=7f9bff22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n懶理Mandy Lieu近來高調出山，自拍出po同網友分享生活點滴。"},{"pid":"24273b7d11aa5c723193bb3a60f77e7bd1b9ee12","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"洗米嫂最強後盾全家撐<br />\n<br />\n為洗米華誕了兩女，跟洗米華跟前妻所生的兒子，亦視如己出，一家五口一直相安無事，自從Mandy Lieu做了洗米華的人肉座墊後，從此風起雲湧，Mandy Lieu為洗米華火速誕三名子女，雖然人在英國但動作多多，一度有傳洗米嫂放棄要離婚，早前盛傳Mandy Lieu於去年收3億分手費，承諾長駐英國、低調生活，而另一邊廂正印洗米嫂亦開心晒全家福，以為搶米戰結束，峰迴路轉，突然Mandy Lieu同洗米華影到在泰國合體漫步沙灘，明顯未斬纜。"},{"pid":"93e784919640e32200b13c877af6ff0055c6fb7d","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/heidi.honey_120262378_1024741464613457_3982388778950200085_n_7398011015f72dc4ca8769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fheidi.honey_120262378_1024741464613457_3982388778950200085_n_7398011015f72dc4ca8769.jpg&h=ff42c1f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢日洗米嫂同大家分享，拆走假眼睫毛的真面目見大家，獲網民大讚後生咗﹗"},{"pid":"9b3ad8a147015c0e11dbe35f99b715ebe430ecbf","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"洗米嫂自爆刻意留下臉上雀斑，因為&hellip;.<br />\nMandy Lieu連番高調晒同洗米華未斬纜，最近又高調出山，為英國雜誌撰寫文章，由最強小三變才女，不過洗米嫂未有作出任何回應，近日，洗米嫂出po晒拆去假眼睫毛的直面目示人，留言：「享受沒眼睫毛的我，哈哈。」獲得網民讚夠自然，看來更年輕，但有網民錯重點，留意到洗米嫂臉上的雀斑，又人大讚添了幾分可愛，亦有人提到做激光清走雀斑，洗米嫂神回：「其實我曾經都試過做光打咗啲雀斑，但我老公要求要我留番啲雀斑，哈哈」一句「老公要求我」就火速K.O.最強小三Mandy Lieu，講到底，正如洗米華當年一句「周太只得一個」﹗高低立見﹗"},{"pid":"da9ee7be1e97ed105660688f0cb9888a0eafb781","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/heidi.honey_120199828_127468455437736_282070540388508828_n_2634080615f72deaae61c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fheidi.honey_120199828_127468455437736_282070540388508828_n_2634080615f72deaae61c2.jpg&h=d6e5ace9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同女兒合照，被網民讚似姊妹多過母女。"},{"pid":"e6301a69574ca8ff387830df0bd1fdaf1851b87b","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/fd84fba9-95fb-47da-86ba-82aba58d7447_72430675f72dc5b28da8-983x1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Ffd84fba9-95fb-47da-86ba-82aba58d7447_72430675f72dc5b28da8-983x1024.jpeg&h=c9931177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不經意的提及老公洗米華，名正言順，大婆二奶地位高低，一眼望清﹗"},{"pid":"70e1b14edf24f8f822f02da7b2cd465ce18b4d15","tid":2222742,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0ac990dd-b366-49dd-ba72-f01e5a9d6cc0_2659548805f72dcdd77796.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F0ac990dd-b366-49dd-ba72-f01e5a9d6cc0_2659548805f72dcdd77796.jpeg&h=cbd8f0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/heidi.honey_117888579_658055521550070_8146275537705026832_n_15632015925f72dcac26184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fheidi.honey_117888579_658055521550070_8146275537705026832_n_15632015925f72dcac26184.jpg&h=185e2fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在IG大晒同華哥合照，以及溫馨全家福，最強小三要行埋一邊。"},{"pid":"625a07f5c51b8b00899e926e1ad0f6f556297fb6","tid":2222742,"uid":48631,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"一句「老公要求我」就火速K.O.最強小三Mandy Lieu<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKo左d咩❓😅"},{"pid":"9fab056e579c8aa70ea550af17cec35d69afa10f","tid":2222742,"uid":56716,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"咁都有得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMandy：「其實我曾經都試過要求戴套，但華哥要求要我地打真軍話要我同佢生仔，哈哈」"},{"pid":"1fdedc9e0e47b9f6088fbb3ec45278fc92ace95c","tid":2222742,"uid":294121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"睇黎mandy既床上功夫好到家<br />\n馴服到個男人死心塌地"},{"pid":"338c293152e8944beb80a7f23be182a250f23c1e","tid":2222742,"uid":118647,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"呢對夫妻撚煩<br />\n<br />\n男人有錢屌下閪都咁多聲氣<br />\n<br />\n唔係條佬養佢佢有今日既生活咩<br />\n<br />\n邊個莊閒都未識分"},{"pid":"ded7429bd368db4dc355ec72b187daf1ec59c4c8","tid":2222742,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"ko個9歲有咩咁巴閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ab9942c7bcf56b597e11585ecd01dff14ba9d6","tid":2222742,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"講咁多<br />\n一張相就K.O.<br />\n我係男人實揀Mandy<br />\n正室成日曬到啡炭咁<br />\n有時染到一生金毛着白色裙<br />\n真係將最唔夾嘅嘢放晒嚮全身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSKQUVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSKQUVq.jpg&h=7fa56269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coS3vud.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoS3vud.jpg&h=632e69a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd232083bb27b96c5f1d5f8e0fc3c3ef1bd0d331","tid":2222742,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T10:03:03.000Z","msg":"Mix真係讓半球